	(2343,237,'flexible_content_blocks_0_text','Todays world demands constant impact. Deep, meaningful, stop-them-in-their- tracks impact. And whether you have a few hundred followers on Twitter or mil- lions of rabid fans doesnt change the fact that you only have a small window to capture their attention. Lets face it, your audience doesnt want static and singular; they want experiences that make them laugh, cry, and stop everything to tell their friends. And they want those experiences all the time.\r\nThats where we come in.\r\n\r\nWe are an agency focused on creating sustained impact through a consistent, open dialogue between you and your audience. How do we do it? Simple. We make good work. Then we make more. And we dont stop. We believe that good work leads to great results, happy clients, and happy employees. Lets talk about how our work can work for you'),
