	(2563,240,'flexible_content_blocks_3_positions_0_description','<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<h2>Studio Manager</h2>\r\nResponsibilities include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Reception</li>\r\n 	<li>General administrative tasks, office management, maintenance, and organization</li>\r\n 	<li>Upkeep of office supplies, equipment, and kitchen sundries (snacks &amp; drinks!)</li>\r\n 	<li>Managing relationships with vendors, tech support, accounts and subscriptions</li>\r\n 	<li>Scheduling and management of multiple calendars</li>\r\n 	<li>Administrative and accounting tasks including independent contractor management and weekly expense reports</li>\r\n 	<li>Assist the project manager and accounting team in project invoicing</li>\r\n 	<li>Mac and Google Suite proficient</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe ideal candidate will be someone who enjoys working with creative people, is friendly, outgoing, confident, organized and able to follow direction and work independently. Strong verbal and written communication skills and attention to detail are required. Must have the desire to learn in a fast-paced environment! Relevant experience would be preferred, and knowledge of  or interest in  the design world is useful, but not essential.\r\n\r\n<strong>Please send your application to <a href=\"mailto:info@heavydoesit.com\">info@heavydoesit.com</a></strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),
